### AI RPG API Testing
### Use Ctrl+Shift+P -> "Rest Client: Send Request" or click "Send Request" above each request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7777
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hello

### Get Current Player
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/player

### Create New Player
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/player
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "name": "Test Hero",
    "attributes": {
        "strength": 15,
        "dexterity": 12,
        "constitution": 14,
        "intelligence": 13,
        "wisdom": 11,
        "charisma": 10
    }
}

### Get All Players
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/players

### Get Attribute Definitions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attributes

### Update Player Attributes
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/player/attributes
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "attributes": {
        "strength": 16,
        "wisdom": 13
    }
}

### Modify Player Health (Damage)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/player/health
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "amount": -5,
    "reason": "orc attack"
}

### Modify Player Health (Healing)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/player/health
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "amount": 3,
    "reason": "healing potion"
}

### Level Up Player
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/player/levelup

### Generate Attributes (Standard Array)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/player/generate-attributes
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "method": "standard"
}

### Generate Attributes (Rolled)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/player/generate-attributes
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "method": "rolled"
}

### Get Chat History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/history

### Clear Chat History
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/history

### Send Chat Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "messages": [
        {
            "role": "user",
            "content": "I want to start a fantasy adventure!"
        }
    ]
}

### Test Config Page
GET {{baseUrl}}/config
